      "text": "C'est la fin.",
      "imagePrompt": "In a hidden courtyard, Avril faces the viewer standing before the last oak tree, sunlight breaking through the clouds above for the first time, illuminating the green leaves and marking the end of the grey steampunk era. Wide shot, eye-level. Warm golden sunlight through parting clouds, hopeful and transformative mood.",
